title: 19: Failure to ship
description: Apple was known for seldom pre-announcing and almost always shipping on time, so what’s going on with AirPods and Apple Watch and iPhone supply this year? Also, Microsoft comes gunning for MacBook Pro.
itunes:author: Michael Gartenberg, Rene Ritchie, Serenity Caldwell
itunes:subtitle: Apple was known for seldom pre-announcing and almost always shipping on time, so what’s going on with AirPods and Apple Watch and iPhone supply this year? Also, Microsoft comes gunning for MacBook Pro.
